						               													<description>Form a unit of three up and coming idols from 765 Production and aim to have as many fans as possible by the time the final stage comes around. Form a deeper bond with your unit as a producer by winning stages and completing jobs. Luck is important in this competitive industry. Stage and job cards require stat check rolls according to the affection of your idols. If you succeed, they are added to your deck and often raise your idols' affection. When their affection reaches its maximum level they become awakened, upgrading to more powerful stats and effects.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Winning stages is a battle between producers attempting to have the most appeal. In turn order, players select one of three stages they would like to participate in for the round. From left to right the stages are resolved, allowing players to play as many cards with the appeal keyword as possible from their hand to gain appeal according to their idols stats. The winner gains affection and fans, while the loser may suffer penalties. The player with the most fans by the end of the game is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
